{"tid":2049081,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"恒指公司稱　現認定阿里必入恒指仍言之尚早","createTime":"2020-06-03T08:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-03T09:11:14.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5d9b7372dce2c547247915fb7a679b8fff8990","tid":2049081,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2655000/2656381/998810529_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2655000%2F2656381%2F998810529_1024.png&h=4bdc808b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恆指公司在新一篇網誌中表示，雖然將於８月的季檢開始考慮納入同股不同權（ＷＶＲ）及第二上巿公司，但現在便認定市值逾4萬億元的阿里巴巴（09988）必然晉身恒指成分股，始終言之尚早。恆指顧問委員會將對恆指公司提供的選擇進行分析，經仔細商討敲定成份股變換決定。阿里3時15分報194.9元，上升0.7%。<br />\n<br />\n除了市值比現已屬藍籌的騰訊（00700）還要高，阿里每日成交額逾40億港元，為本地規模最大及其中一間成交最活躍的上巿公司。<br />\n<br />\n恒指公司又表示，恆指作為市場重要指標，用途非常廣泛及複雜，要改變編算方法著實不易，但<span style=\"color: red;\">不代表法則不能改變或一成不變</span>，將成分股的選股範圍擴大至同股不同權及第二上巿公司，是反映市場狀況及用家需求，又指樂於聆聽市場聲音，在回應社會變化的同時，亦會致力維護不同持份者的利益。<br />\n<br />\n市場早看好阿里最終能染藍，除因市值屬港股最高，納入阿里亦有助恒指更能反映新經濟重要性日益增加的現實。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<em>高盛發表報告指，假設三間公司納入恒指，阿里和美團的權重將達封頂上限的5%，並各有約13億美元（約100億港元）被動追入兩間公司股份，成為下次季檢大贏家。而小米則會佔恒指權重1%，被動資金有2.5億美元流入。</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴巴5%<br />\n美團5%<br />\n小米1%<br />\n騰訊10%<br />\n係時候諗吓邊隻股要降<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0888f59ba97f063b397cfc33a98badc403911d44","tid":2049081,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咪又係升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6031d504d78ba92826f0840ff79c2bbd9f1f99","tid":2049081,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0888f59ba97f063b397cfc33a98badc403911d44","tid":2049081,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咪又係升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"其實恆指未來必定變做睇ATM頭黎上落<br />\n所以預計大陸佬可以話冇我地中國公司,你恆指撚有得升咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca7d9c28c069e9b2676b47c2f48b093e23c3339f","tid":2049081,"uid":321977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e6031d504d78ba92826f0840ff79c2bbd9f1f99","tid":2049081,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0888f59ba97f063b397cfc33a98badc403911d44","tid":2049081,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:24:48.000Z","msg":"是但啦，咪又係升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:27:42.000Z","msg":"其實恆指未來必定變做睇ATM頭黎上落<br />\n所以預計大陸佬可以話冇我地中國公司,你恆指撚有得升咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dllm.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"未來未來先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cb14476cce1f4fc935ba01de6b3e773f263630","tid":2049081,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:06:23.000Z","msg":"未夠貴。等佢上250先納入等基金etf MPF 齊齊接"},{"pid":"f9ba0a144a3c90adaeecef2c79a6676ec2a8bcd6","tid":2049081,"uid":356101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即係入硬啦"}]}